highlights.text: Arijit Singh has the most spots on Top Songs Guwahati. Kesariya is the highest at #4.
Pyaar Hota Kayi Baar Hai (From "Tu Jhoothi Main Makkaar") by Pritam, Arijit Singh, Amitabh Bhattacharya, and Charan is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Guwahati, up 43 spots at #30.
Die For You - Remix by The Weeknd and Ariana Grande is the highest new entry on Top Songs Guwahati at #52.
